# The Untied House — Design System

## Typography

All headings MUST use Newsreader italic via the `.font-heading` utility class.

| Element | Class | Notes |
|---------|-------|-------|
| Headings (h1–h3, display text) | `font-heading` | Sets `font-family: 'Newsreader', serif; font-style: italic;` |
| Body / UI text | `font-body` | Sets `font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;` |
| Labels, tags, buttons | `font-body` + `uppercase tracking-[0.2em–0.4em] text-[10px]` | Small caps treatment |

Never use raw `font-['Newsreader:...']` inline classes — always use `.font-heading`.

### Heading sizes (responsive)

- **Hero (h1)**: `text-5xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-[10rem]`
- **Section (h2)**: `text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-8xl`
- **Card / Sub (h3)**: `text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl`

## Colors

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `text-primary` | `#1c1917` | Headings, primary text |
| `text-secondary` | `#57534e` | Nav links, supporting text |
| `text-muted` | `#78716c` | Footer labels, captions |
| `text-subtle` | `#a8a29e` | Form labels, placeholders |
| `text-inverse` | `#fbf2c4` | Text on dark backgrounds |
| `bg-brand` | `#fbf2c4` | Page background |
| `bg-dark` | `#1c1c1a` | Dark section backgrounds |

## Components

- **Inputs**: `font-heading` + underline-only border style
- **Buttons (primary)**: `bg-dark text-inverse font-body uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px]`
- **Buttons (outline)**: `border border-[#d6d3d1] text-secondary font-body uppercase`
- **Labels**: `font-body uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] text-subtle font-bold`

## Scroll Animations

Use the `<Reveal>` component to wrap sections for fade-up-on-scroll. Supports `delay` prop (ms).

```tsx
<Reveal delay={100}>
  <section>...</section>
</Reveal>
```

## Page Transitions

Handled automatically by `<PageTransition>` in Root.tsx — smooth opacity + translateY fade between routes.
